{"tid":810243,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲仔，開始唔再淨睇啲無理頭爆谷戲","createTime":"2018-09-07T19:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T03:52:41.000Z","uid":860,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"66befb892db4afb4d30bed14fb9f8bbc27c866e6","tid":810243,"uid":860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:37:59.000Z","msg":"由細到大都淨係睇啲動作片，搞笑片，科幻片<br />\n合家歡爆谷片咁<br />\n但最近自己走去睇王家衛<br />\n一開頭唔太慣，但慢慢就睇得明佢拍啲野講緊乜<br />\n唔係想話認叻扮成熟<br />\n但發現人大左真係會唔同<br />\n當然，啲戇鳩搞笑片都會繼續去睇，有時真係唔想諗太多野睇啲無理頭笑下都幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499a50aec458a6f0e6705cb58d20e14fded13a1c","tid":810243,"uid":127272,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/034215_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F034215_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=7b518cd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/034217_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F034217_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=700fabd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/034219_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F08%2F034219_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=40955eda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"087525d684ba8540da4deb0ca7e97a51beb647d0","tid":810243,"uid":124491,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"499a50aec458a6f0e6705cb58d20e14fded13a1c","tid":810243,"uid":127272,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/08/034215_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f